{"tid":2005491,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"德國戰線 一連八場Online Forum正式上線!","createTime":"2020-05-07T06:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T09:26:08.000Z","uid":265707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c37061d57f11ee67ba61a1271d0635d68e71399e","tid":2005491,"uid":265707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0FmiPBj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0FmiPBj.jpg&h=763f6afb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地係一group係德國嘅香港人，眾所周知<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國</span></span></span></span>，乃至<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">成個歐盟</span></span></span></span>都係奶共嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好感激海外嘅港人一直都心繫呢個家，係唔同國家搞左好多遊行、集會，將香港人嘅抗爭事跡帶到去歐洲國家入面，對上一次其他手足係德國搞嘅聯署非常之成功，亦順利將香港嘅議題擺上德國議會討論，但另一邊廂德國政府仍然對香港嘅議題採取<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">曖昧</span></span>態度，我地深知呢一場革命唔會一時三刻就完，所以要令到相距我地千里，再加埋一直同支國有緊密經貿合作嘅歐洲人同我地企埋同一陣線，靠嘅唯有係我地一點一滴<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">深耕細作</span></span>，將我地嘅政治理念慢慢滲透入去，令佢地睇穿支國糖衣包裝嘅經濟成果，見到佢地背後嘅腐敗同對人權嘅威脅。<br />\n<br />\n所以我地成立左<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Wir f&uuml;r Hongkong </span></span>呢個組織，目的就係要用我地一直被極權支那政府打壓自由同侵蝕法治嘅經歷，啟發番其他國家嘅人去<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">反思自己國家嘅民主進程</span></span></span>，我地<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔想</span>單純做一個<span style=\"font-size: large;\">民宣機器</span>，因此相比起速食，我地更希望透過<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">論述嚴謹、有深度</span></span>嘅文章、影像同論壇等方式，令外國人將香港嘅情況，連繫到自己國家，繼而有實質嘅行動同思維上嘅改變。我地平時都會定期係我地嘅網站上面撰文，主題不限於香港，亦都包括國際關注嘅議題，希望盡可能吸引到更加多嘅potential audience，去加入我地反共嘅陣線。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t9NFiyo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft9NFiyo.png&h=c49a383e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n有興趣大家都可以去我地個網站睇下，同埋記得share 比你地身邊嘅外國人睇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://wirfuerhongkong.org/posts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwirfuerhongkong.org%2Fposts%2F&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdSlkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=84552d4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wirfuerhongkong.org/posts/</a><br />\n<br />\n自上年九月以嚟我地係德國都有份組織大大小小嘅活動，包括每星期一次八場係Laidak （一間係德國政治圈出名bar）以反送中示威為題嘅演講，十一月份柏林圍牆倒下三十週年反共反極權集會，同埋二月嘅時候係柏林搞左個香港抗爭記錄片嘅放映活動，接住落嚟，我地趁住肺炎大家都要居家隔離嘅時候，搞左一連串由<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">四月至七月</span></span>，以「社會契約」為主題嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Online Forum</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">每兩星期一次</span></span>，而且呢八場Forum嘅主題唔單止講香港，仲包括德國、法國、南韓等國家，務求令到唔同國家嘅人都能夠代入自己國家嘅處景，再將香港嘅情況連繫一齊。前兩次我地已經講左德國同法國，以武漢肺炎為核心，帶到去佢地分別最關心嘅氣候同埋選舉議題上，而嚟緊第三場 5月14號星期四我地即將會講香港集會自由同釋法嘅問題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H3Dw9N1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH3Dw9N1.jpg&h=b2403585&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/265179531297209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F265179531297209%2F&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdSlkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=61adfca1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/265179531297209/</a><br />\n雖然嚟緊呢一場係德文，但之後亦都會有英文，所以大家記得follow 我地嘅Telegram Channel緊貼我地嘅消息，未來仲有五場Forum希望大家可以盡量spread 開去話比外國人知！<br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"https://t.me/wirfuerhongkong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwirfuerhongkong&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdSlkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=dc84a9b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wirfuerhongkong</a><br />\n<br />\n以下係我地各項Social Media 嘅link 希望大家可以幫手Follow同Share 出去，我地依家Followers嚴重不足宣傳效果好有限，希望可以先鞏固番多啲香港人，再推出去國際！<br />\nWebsite: <a href=\"https://wirfuerhongkong.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwirfuerhongkong.org%2F&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdSlkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=dbdd45c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wirfuerhongkong.org/</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/w4hongkong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fw4hongkong&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdSlkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=ce5ea570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/w4hongkong</a><br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wirfuerhongkong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwirfuerhongkong%2F&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdSlkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=895e1260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wirfuerhongkong/</a><br />\nYoutube: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6mzpB-vYoKKCyWqDtySGWQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC6mzpB-vYoKKCyWqDtySGWQ&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdSlkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=6fa37206\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6mzpB-vYoKKCyWqDtySGWQ</a>"},{"pid":"054e6cc77fca3a58f0591ed737bdaec18ae7cf45","tid":2005491,"uid":265707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:41:39.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"db1ce4197c22a9717fe4a7e157236506516fc1ca","tid":2005491,"uid":265707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:41:57.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5f36121df03e21ead1717a33aaf68764773d87b9","tid":2005491,"uid":265707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:44:14.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c7ac4f98826a5c2b2fdcd5e6a01f223f5cc45020","tid":2005491,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:44:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0695f38b72cad8b58bf4919ddb4642179c5de2c","tid":20054